}{}$^2$\end{document}</tex-math></inline-formula></italic> can simultaneously estimate the subclonal CNA and SNV genotypes, the overlapping relationship of CNA and SNV, the subclonal assignments of cells and the tumor evolutionary tree. In comparison with existing methods on synthetic and real tumor data, <italic toggle="yes">BiTSC<inline-formula><tex-math notation="LaTeX" id="ImEquation19">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
