}{}$^2$\end{document}</tex-math></inline-formula></italic> shows high accuracy in genotype recovery, subclonal assignment and clone tree reconstruction. It is worth noting that <italic toggle="yes">BiTSC<inline-formula><tex-math notation="LaTeX" id="ImEquation20">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
